### Blog Content Generation API - HTTP Test Requests
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tools

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json

### 1. Test Sanity Connection
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/test-sanity

### 2. Get Available Categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/blog/generate

### 3. Generate Blog Post - Basic (Sovereign AI)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/blog/generate
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "category": "Sovereign AI",
  "publishStatus": "draft"
}

### 4. Generate Blog Post - With Specific Topic
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/blog/generate
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "category": "Sovereign AI",
  "topic": "AI governance frameworks",
  "publishStatus": "draft"
}

### 5. Generate Blog Post - LMS Scaling Category
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/blog/generate
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
